OL,6,FA thief has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a courier who died trying to
OL,8,Fstop his delivery van being stolen.
OL,10,FClaudiu Carol-Kondor, 42, was run over
OL,11,Fby 32-year-old Mark Ross while
OL,12,Fdelivering parcels for Amazon.
OL,14,FMr Kondor, from Sheffield, died from
OL,15,Fcrush injuries after he clung to his
OL,16,Fvan as Ross drove off and hit two
OL,17,Fparked cars on 20 August last year.
