OL,6,FLeeds Crown Court heard Ross reached
OL,7,Fspeeds of almost 60mph on residential
OL,8,Fstreets and swerved erratically from
OL,9,Fside to side before hitting stationary
OL,10,FMinis.
OL,12,FProsecutors said the defendant was
OL,13,Ftrying to "get rid" of Mr Kondor as he
OL,14,Fhung onto the van from the open
OL,15,Fpassenger door.
OL,17,FRoss admitted manslaughter but denied
OL,18,Fmurdering Mr Kondor, claiming he was
OL,19,Funaware Mr Kondor was holding on. He
OL,20,Fwas found guilty after around a day of
OL,21,Fjury deliberations.
