OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Det Ch
OL,7,FInsp James Entwistle, of West
OL,8,FYorkshire Police, said: "It is truly
OL,9,Fheart-breaking that the life of an
OL,10,Fhonest hard-working man has been
OL,11,Fsnatched away by the cruel and callous
OL,12,Factions of Mark Ross."
OL,14,FMr Kondor had been delivering a
OL,15,Fpackage to an address in Alliance
OL,16,FStreet, Armley, shortly before 7pm
OL,17,Fwhen Mark Ross jumped into the
OL,18,Fdriver's seat of his silver Ford
OL,19,FTransit Cargo van.
