OL,6,FRoss claimed he was unaware of Mr
OL,7,FKondor hanging onto the van and said
OL,8,Fhe had crashed into the parked car
OL,9,Fafter losing control on speed bumps.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said Ross had collided
OL,12,Fwith the car deliberately to knock him
OL,13,Foff.
OL,15,FIn his closing speech, Mr Harrison
OL,16,Fsaid Ross showed a "complete disregard
OL,17,Fand even contempt" for Mr Kondor's
OL,18,Flife.
